  first, convert the slideshow into standard smugmug style
  	 (Customize... Gallery Style... Smugmug (default))
  then, http://help.smugmug.com/customer/portal/articles/93254#slideshow
  	click on a photo to enter lightbox mode
	click on the share button below the photo
	choose Gallery tab
	choose Embed sub-tab
	scroll down to adjust options
	copy-paste the HTML code below;
	hand-edit to reduce width and height to 600x400
  then, convert it back to slideshow for the site
  -->
